SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to ADD CHILE and REMOVE ST. KITTS AND NEVIS from the list of countries and territories whose citizens are exempt from the TEMPORARY RESIDENT VISA requirement for travel to Canada.
